headline.main: DARLAN IN PARIS FOR NEW PARLEYS; Latest 'Collaboration' Talks Already Begun With Nazi Envoys to Lyon Fair LA ROCQUE GETS NEW POST Former Croix de Feu Head Is 'Charged With Missions' in Petain's Office

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Oct. 1 -- Admiral Francois Darlan, the Vice Premier, has left for Paris on one of his periodical visits.
abstract: Apptd in charge of missions by Marshal Petain
